{"tid":1977029,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「白癡」所為，拒絕上當 - 李碧華","createTime":"2020-04-17T15:51:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T17:06:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c70bb4fbf493ecc2fdcb42deaa700747344b3129","tid":1977029,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T15:51:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200417/20901252/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200417%2F20901252%2F&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppetlAIsOV5GGnQ0mU6qdzh4w%3D&h=2854a843\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200417%2F20901252%2F&h=b1cc51ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200417/20901252/</a><br />\n<br />\n「白癡」所為，拒絕上當 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200417/large/1587021908_6f42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200417%2Flarge%2F1587021908_6f42.jpg&h=91c6a7e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n路透社<br />\n<br />\n「美國總統特朗普宣佈，停止資助世界衛生組織，指世衛隱瞞武漢肺炎疫情之嚴重性，而且應對疫情失當。」──侵侵閂水喉，大快人心。<br />\n<br />\n美國納稅人每年給世衛4到5億美元（31.2至39億港元），但世衛中人因被中共收買，未能負起基本責任且偏袒中國，謊報瞞報遲報還擦鞋獻媚，瘟疫全球大流行，重重錯誤危害眾生，必須被追究。<br />\n<br />\n埃塞俄比亞的譚德塞是中共黑奴（不是「歧視」而是「鄙視」），代世衛收取中國二千萬美元捐款，這筆錢不知是公是私下落如何，但黑奴高調稱頌，實超級昂貴的口罩（揞口費）。即使全球最大網絡請願平台，有「要求譚德塞下台！」活動，百萬人連署，但比不上閂水喉應棍。<br />\n<br />\n這回抗疫成績顯著的如台灣、韓國、香港&hellip;&hellip;都在眾目睽睽下，發揮自強保健團結抗疫力量──因為大家都不相信中國大陸任何新聞訊息和數字，全靠自救。<br />\n<br />\n只有習大大企圖改寫歷史，以「醫療外交」塑造救世主假象，遣外交官向各國游說，要求「讚美中國抗疫」，德、美&hellip;&hellip;拒絕上當，形容為「白癡」所為。你以為人人都像塞爾維亞總統，迎接中國醫療隊及口罩等物資時，親吻五星旗且全國廣告「感謝您習大哥」般厚顏嗎？賣吻、賣笑、賣菊花、賣良知&hellip;&hellip;會永垂不朽的。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"86ec16b600d44842f551f02c1e3089a266890069","tid":1977029,"uid":265416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T16:04:33.000Z","msg":"李碧華都動真火"},{"pid":"9a3d928d82c17bbb24ce98761dcf14e652937140","tid":1977029,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T17:06:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}